subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament (Women)
lead_paragraph: Connecticut steamrolled Southern University but lower seeds like No. 10 Vermont, No. 11 San Diego State and No. 12 Wisconsin-Green Bay had the first upsets of the tournament.
